title: Bob Boilen And Gaelynn Lea: What's In Your Tiny Desk? (R)
description: NPR Music host Bob Boilen talks about the Tiny Desk Contest and winner Gaelynn Lea plays two of her songs. Then naturally the two play a game about things you find in a desk. This Episode originally aired June 3, 2016.
